== Automatic scaling ==

=== Summary ===

This feature would help users setup rules to automatically scale out their applications based on their load data.

=== Owner ===

* Name: [[User:LHornyak Laszlo Hornyak]]
* Email: <lhornyak@radhet.com>


=== Current status ===
* Status: proposal
* Last updated on {{REVISIONYEAR}}-{{REVISIONMONTH}}-{{REVISIONDAY}} by {{REVISIONUSER}}

=== Detailed Description ===

This feature will address the needs of applications and systems scaling out. When a certain resource usage goes over or below a certain user-defined limit, some an action would take place, which is typically starting and/or stopping a VM from a pool.
Such conditions could be:
* disk usage
* free disk space
* network usage
* CPU usage

=== Benefit to oVirt ===

This feature allows oVirt to automatically scale applications based on their resource usage.

